otocol": "https", "ext": "mp4", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "resolution": "1080x1934", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format_id": "9", "format": "9 - 1080x1934"}], "title": "Video by pagetkagy", "description": "Science proved THIS changes reality ⬇️\nㅤ\nIn the Double Slit Experiment, particles don’t behave like solid matter until they’re observed. Before observation, they exist as probabilities. The act of observing collapses those probabilities into a single outcome. This isn’t philosophy - it’s measured PHYSICS.\nㅤ\nYour brain works the same way. Your subconscious attention acts as the observer, constantly collapsing one version of reality out of many possible ones. When your focus is trained on threat, lack, or resistance, that’s the timeline that keeps rendering.\nㅤ\nThe Delayed Choice Experiment went even further, showing that observation can influence outcomes backward in time. Which explains why, when your internal state shifts, past events suddenly make sense differently and opportunities appear where nothing existed before.\nㅤ\nYou’re not manifesting incorrectly. You’re observing consistently. Change the observer, and the reality being rendered has no choice but to change with it.\nㅤ\nFollow @pagetkagy to train the observer that shapes your reality ✨\nㅤ\n#quantumphysics #observereffect #doubleslitexperiment #timelineshift #selfconcept #identityshift #scienceandmind", "duration": 95.99, "timestamp": 1772024485, "uploader_id": "179593201", "uploader": "Paget Kagy | Quantum Energy Coach", "channel": "pagetkagy", "like_count": 28594, "comment_count": 507, "comments": [{"author": "robert.rulison66", "author_id": "1902709211", "id": "17943789204152520", "text": "Uhhhhh..,what?", "timestamp": 1775151601}, {"author": "klvn0", "author_id": "176383186", "id": "17971615056033176", "text": "Consciousness is not the observer, \"observer\" is a historical term and misleading in common English contexts. An \"observer in quantum/physical context is any physical system that interacts with a quantum system in a way that records or correlates with its state, like a detector, a photographic plate, a gas molecule, even a rock. Consciousness plays no part at all. This whole post is based on incorrect, foundational understanding. Nothing was proved about manifesting at all.", "timestamp": 1775135034}, {"author": "simonherfet", "author_id": "9750721656", "id": "17962496061060307", "text": "🙌", "timestamp": 1775124367}, {"author": "janicemasters1", "author_id": "3402074136", "id": "18074003918199588", "text": "Yes yes yes that's why ALREADY is magic!!!", "timestamp": 1775087311}, {"author": "ap.ammala", "author_id": "35369408", "id": "17913666483162749", "text": "👏👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1775060038}, {"author": "jcleaze", "author_id": "51476267", "id": "18093624590129600", "text": "I tried explaining this to an ex who would play Dr Strange in her mind lol", "timestamp": 1775050367}, {"author": "abdimajid_suleiman", "author_id": "26683069127", "id": "17921828457282567", "text": "How can i change my frequency?", "timestamp": 1775030890}, {"author": "erik_v83", "author_id": "31713000", "id": "18070900730276081", "text": "Identity", "timestamp": 1775018490}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641757331_18568654555009202_5424564394734466725_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p640x640_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMDcyeDE5MjAuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHscETUFBwQW1mKbjKnTEKcQMmefHAWmOY1ZmwwVguVaaz5O2tIgkmG67Em65fC0is&_nc_ohc=2dyYjE1LUgkQ7kNvwGxi-E6&_nc_gid=KzLddJXg